name: Merry Christmas, Everyone!
description: I took the photo back in 2019 on a christmas eve, inside the Bellagio Hotel, Las Vegas. It was the last christmas I spend with my family, because they all live in United States, while I'm in Indonesia. Hopefully I can renew my visa so I can travel back to see my family. That's it about me. Now I wish you all the best for you and your family. Happy holiday, merry christmas, and GBU!
